archimate:DataObject.name: RevenueAssuranceAssessmentResult
archimate:DataObject.documentation: The outcome of a RevenueAssuranceAssessment. The outcome may be a recommendation to refine a RevenueAssuranceParameter; a RevenueAssuranceObjective; RevenueAssuranceConsequence; RevenueAssuranceApplicability or the identification of a RevenueAssuranceTrend.
